<body class="market-US">
    <div class="gloss">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div id="container">
                <div class="content background game-background-wordscramble">
                    <div id="intro">
                        <h1>QuiBids Games</h1>
                        <div id="intro-text">
                            <h2 class="bold game-heading">Looking to win some FREE BIDS? You've come to the right place.					<span>In QuiBids Games, you can choose from a great selection of games and win tons of bids!</span></h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <div id="sections">
                        <h2 class="bold game-heading2">Playing QuiBids Games is as easy as 1, 2, 3.</h2>
                        <div class="module">
                            <div class="content">
                                <p><img src="~/Content/Games_img/gameplay-step1.jpg" /></p>
                                <h3 class="bold orange one">Win a Gameplay!</h3>
                                <p>
                                    <span class="bold"><b>Want to know more about QuiBids Games and Gameplays?</b></span>
                                    The short story: you earn them by winning Gameplay Auctions. The long story: well, we recommend you check out our <a href="">Help pages</a> for more information.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div><!--module-->
                        <div class="module">
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>
                                    <img src="~/Content/Games_img/gameplay-step2.jpg" />
                                </p>
                                <h3 class="bold orange two">Choose your Game!</h3>
                                <p>
                                    <span class="bold"><b>When it comes to scoring free bids, you've got plenty of options.</b></span>
                                    Flick through our assortment of Games for your favorite, or try something new. Be sure to check back here every now and then, as we're always working on new games for you to enjoy!
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div><!--module-->
                        <div class="module">
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>
                                    <img src="~/Content/Games_img/gameplay-step3.jpg" />
                                </p>
                                <h3 class="bold orange three">Earn Bids!</h3>
                                <p>
                                    <span class="bold"><b>When you play QuiBids Games, you get free Voucher Bids.</b></span>
                                    It's that simple. When you're done, gather up those fresh bids and jump back into the next auction!                            <span class="emphasize">
                                        (
                                        No purchase necessary. See <a href="/en/help/game_rules.php">rules</a> for details.															)
                                    </span>
                                </p>
                                <p class="button">
                                    <a href="/en/landing/" class="buttons standard orange">Join now to play!</a>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div><!--module-->
                    </div><!--3-sections-->

